{"tid":603037,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"<AN>億萬遺跡，刪檔封測開始","createTime":"2018-03-23T11:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T10:02:32.000Z","uid":21154,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22264a4a156a83215f212948131224a5f16bd9d1","tid":603037,"uid":21154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:32:31.000Z","msg":"重新出post<br />\n開始左可以試玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 易家server無問題<br />\n<br />\n香港遊戲開發團隊 Skytree Digital Limited 宣佈，開發中的領地爭奪型對戰遊戲《億萬遺跡》將於香港時間 2018 年 3 月 23 日至 3 月 25 日將進行刪檔封測。玩家將在遊戲舞台中使用卡片來與其他對手競爭地盤、收取過路費，設法成為最終的贏家。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/192707_785ffbaf30380620d8bf56dc94faa582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F192707_785ffbaf30380620d8bf56dc94faa582.jpg&h=88e32462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《億萬遺跡》的故事由陰險的遺跡神奪去雞王國開始。雞王國的王子里查必須肩負起拯救雞王國的重任，透過參與「競技場」對戰，贏取太陽幣直至足夠贖回雞王國為止。競技場是由正直的創世神所創立的比賽，每局都是鬥智鬥力的公平競爭。競技場的挑戰者會運用各式各樣的強力卡牌來作戰。然而，里查從小嬌生慣養，對競技場比試一竅不通&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n　　另外，當玩家完成 5 局遊戲後會跳至問卷頁面，完成問卷之玩家可獲得 100 鑽石的序號，於遊戲正式上架時兌換。<br />\n <br />\n========================================<br />\n移動與佔地<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/191927_2dd3cff14579b9d9db622e20eaacc971.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F191927_2dd3cff14579b9d9db622e20eaacc971.JPG&h=c7af08a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/191926_2bbdc6ba475f0551d57432ecbd87dbff.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F191926_2bbdc6ba475f0551d57432ecbd87dbff.JPG&h=4d084641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/191926_13d9c5a44f4e84d24fd1f4176da6eafe.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F191926_13d9c5a44f4e84d24fd1f4176da6eafe.JPG&h=3906c10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　玩家的目標是在 18 回合內拚過對手，賺取最多的財產。而要達成這個目標，佔領越多土地就越有利。要佔領土地，可以踏在空地上以獲得新的土地，或是擊敗對手以奪取他的土地。<br />\n <br />\n　　在移動牌左上方的數字表示有機會的步數，左中方的數字表示到達後對敵人土地造成的傷害。在法術牌中，每一張牌的下方都有說明各自的能力。可以巧用法術牌來進行防護 / 攻擊等技能。<br />\n <br />\n　　卡組的組成口訣為 4+1+5，分別為 4張電腦分出的基本牌，1 張相同的專用法術牌以及 5 張專用移動牌。<br />\n <br />\n　　最關鍵的是 5 張專用移動牌，每個角色都會有多款不同有技能的移動牌，玩家需要從中選出 5 張專用移動牌。卡組內會有 15 張牌，當所有牌都用完後，卡牌會被重新抽出。<br />\n <br />\n過路費與破壞敵方建築<br />\n <br />\n　　踏到空地時便可獲得該地，而每回到 / 經過 1 次起點後，所有自己的房屋便會升級，再踏中自己的房屋後可進行下注，把過路費以倍數上升。<br />\n <br />\n　　另外，佔領相連的房屋也會有連結倍數加乘。每間房屋都有血量顯示，當玩家踏到敵人的房屋時，需繳付過路費；但若能把房屋扣到 0，不只可免除過路費，更可即時把房屋搶佔。"},{"pid":"5ca811458d3cf8cf8ceecafdf00afdeee9222853","tid":603037,"uid":21154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"120c6f015ad5f92f9a5d84aeacf90c610f6934e7","tid":603037,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"050cb658f841b3dfdb4f291ca43cb6beca510dd3","tid":603037,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾"},{"pid":"76d13b1f748702f5b574f25b1df4478bc984ee06","tid":603037,"uid":21154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"Google Play Download Link: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/Y7kcXn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FY7kcXn&d=UMigsLiDAYQDA6SGr28idnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=05c9cb78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Y7kcXn</a>"},{"pid":"3124643990499801f4f68a6031f2626047081412","tid":603037,"uid":21154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c914ef9e33422ff84de26b0a3e064d9e0bb23f16","tid":603037,"uid":21154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebf4d7cc8e9f70a6290a11dc1225c181273d033","tid":603037,"uid":21154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}